title: R.I. revenue running 2.9 percent ahead of projections
text: PROVIDENCE, R.I. - - The June opening of a "racino" just across the line in Plainville, Ma., has not siphoned away anywhere near as much Rhode Island casino business as feared."It appears that we may have been too pessimistic about the impact that the opening of the racino in Plainville, Ma., would have on the Twin River Casino in nearby Lincoln, R.I., but I would caution that it is still early in the fiscal year to know [...]> ...
